      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rihta / kad Gaisina met-tehs/ tad tappe ſchee Wihri at-laisti winni/ lihds ar faweein Eh-fekeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet teem no Piſsjahta iſ-eijoht/ un tahti ne nahkoht/ faz-ztja Jahſeps us fawa Namuna Uhſraugu ; Zellees / Dſennees teem Wihreem pakkat/ un tohs panahzis/ fakkins teem : Kadeht effat juhs labhu ar ſaunu at-makfajſchi?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Neggi ſchis irr tas/ is ka mans Kung̅ dſexx/ un pee ta at-minnehs wiꞥſch teescham ( Fahdi Laudis juhs effat)/ juhs effat ſaun darrijschi/ to darriſami.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas panahze winkus/ un fazzija us winneem ſchohs Wahrdus:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija winnt us to : Raphz ruña mansKungs tahdus Wahrdus? Muhschaun tawi Kal-pi ſcho Darbu ne darrihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Reds/ to Nandu/ ko mehs effam atraddufschi muhfu Maisfu Wirṣ-Galla / effam mehs pee tew atkat atneffuschi no Kanāg-na Semmes/ ka tad mehs ſag-fim istawa Kunga NamnuSu-Drabu jeb Seltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pee ka tas no taweem Kal-peem taps atrasts/ tas lai mirſt/ un mehs arri gribbam tawam Kungam par Wehrgeem buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija: Lai tas arridsan ta buht pehz juhſu Wahrdeim / pee ka tas atrasts us angſchu : pee juhfu Te\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee trauzahs/ zehle itweens fawu Ma-Senunes/ un itweens fawu Maisu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch pahrme ta Leela eefahkdams/ un Masaka beigdams/ un teeris tappe Benjaminu atrasts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad pahrplehſe te Dreſbes/ un usfrahwe us fawu Ehseli/ un atg Piſsjahta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Juhda nahze weem Brahſteem Jahſepa mā/ jo wiꞥſch pats tur we un tee nomettehs preekſch Waigu pee Senmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jahſeps faz-teem: Kas tas tahds ko juhs effat darrijschi juhs buhtut finnajschi/ ka Wihrs/ fahds es/ teefchan paredſejs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Juho mehs us mannu Kungu fa ko mehs runnasim/ un k taisnofintees? Deews ir Kalpu Moseegumu atradd mehs effam manna Kunga gi/ tik lab mehs/ ka arri ta tas Bifkeris irr atraste\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiꞥſch ſchani es to ne darriſchu Wihrs/ pee ka tas Bifkeris rats/ tam buhs man par gu buht : Bet juhs eita a\n"
